[0:30 – 0:58] The Engine (Staff-Level Prompt Architecture)

Visual:
System diagram with isolated prompt layers and feedback loops.

On-Screen Text (Sequential Reveal)
System Prompts — Persona & Constraints
Reasoning Prompts — Follow-up Generation
Evaluation Prompts — Scoring & Signal Extraction
Refinement Prompts — Output Optimization
Guardrails — Bias & Consistency Control
Voiceover (Upgraded, Explicit)

“This system is built on layered prompt orchestration—not a single chat flow.

First, system prompts lock the AI into a bounded interviewer persona, defining tone, authority, and domain expectations.

Second, reasoning prompts analyze candidate responses for depth, ambiguity, and risk—then generate targeted follow-ups designed to increase cognitive load.

Third, evaluation prompts score answers across clarity, relevance, confidence, and decision quality—using normalized criteria to ensure consistency.

Fourth, refinement prompts transform raw responses into high-impact alternatives, showing candidates exactly how stronger answers are structured.

Finally, guardrail prompts enforce persona boundaries, mitigate bias, and prevent evaluation drift across sessions.”

